CharNavLinks is the sum of [[Template:CharNavCard|CharNavCard]] and a character's Data Links, to be displayed at the bottom of each character page and in the header of any character subpages. This allows easy navigation back to the main character page as well as quick access to the other subpages under that character. The image displayed is always the character's main portrait.

<pre>
{{#invoke:CharNavLinks 
| main 
}}
</pre>

The image offset and color of the card outline are determined by a table within this module. Offsets are designed to display the character's eyes within the frame, while the outline colors are based on the official character grouping colors in their respective game, where possible.

